

    
         Silence    The silence fills the room.  Eyes fixating on eyes, fingers twitching and bodies swaying... The heaviness in the atmosphere seeps slowly into the people.  They fidget silently.  Are they mute?   There they stand with no reply.  Waiting.  Yet, what do they wait for.  They wait for something to happen.  Unspoken thoughts  drift in the air uneasily.  Some enjoy the golden note while others feel empty.  Silence and Emptiness.  Waiting... 
    
    
